sentences.en: He put in something about the - Supernal Oneness.
sentences.cn: 他说一点天上的一元论.

sentences.en: My name is etched into the substance of a higher world - the Supernal World, they call it.
sentences.cn: 我的名字蚀刻进了更高层界域的实体之中 —— [超然之界], 他们这么称呼.

sentences.en: Put in something about the Supernal Oneness . Don't say a syllable about the Infernal Twoness.
sentences.cn: 说一点天上的一元论,千万别谈地狱的二元论.

sentences.en: The soul, or the principle that we call the soul, is the supernal criticism of the deeds done in the body, which goes perpetually on in the waking mind.
sentences.cn: 灵魂，或者是我们根据准则而所谓的灵魂，是对身体行为的一种超自然的批评，这种超自然的批评永远的存在于我们流动的思想之中。

sentences.en: The supernal ideology will not coexistence with the everyman.
sentences.cn: 超凡的思想是不会与凡夫俗子共存的.
